Introduction

translation) 에서 RNN(Recurrent Neural Networks), LSTM(Long Short-Term  
Memory), Gated Recurrent Neural Networks는 SOTA로 굳건히 자리 잡고 있음.  
ꢀ

sequential nature가지고 있음

Position-wise Feed-Forward Networks  
Each of the layers in our encoder and decoder contains a fully connected feed-forward  
network, which is applied to each position separately and identically.  
https://pozalabs.github.io/transformer/  
While the linear transformations are the same across different positions,  
they use different parameters from layer to layer.
